videos.description: Nebraska comes out of the gates firing with a 42-yard touchdown pass from Adrian Martinez to JD Spielman to put the Cornhuskers up first 7-0.
videos.headline: Nebraska strikes first with quick 42-yard TD

videos.description: Northwestern quarterback Clayton Thorson slings a 24-yard touchdown pass to Flynn Nagel to knot up the score 7-7 in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Northwestern QB darts 21-yard TD

videos.description: Nebraska quarterback Adrian Martinez is blown up by Trae Williams in Northwestern territory. Earnest Brown IV scoops the loose ball and chugs 16 yards to the house for 6.
videos.headline: Northwestern strip sack results in 6

videos.description: Nebraska closes the half with a quick 83-yard scoring drive, capped off by a Devine Ozigbo 12-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Nebraska answers with 12-yard TD before half

videos.description: Northwestern's second half opening drive stalls as quarterback Clayton Thorson airs it out downfield into double coverage and is picked off by Antonio Reed.
videos.headline: Northwestern QB intercepted on deep shot

videos.description: Nebraska running back Maurice Washington shows off his lightning speed by breaking to the edge and scooting into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown, his first of the season.
videos.headline: Nebraska RB cuts to edge for 3-yard TD

videos.description: Clayton Thorson catapults a prayer off his back foot that lands perfectly into the hands of Flynn Nagel, who eludes two tacklers and bolts to the house for a 61-yard Northwestern touchdown.
videos.headline: Thorson-Nagel connect again for 61-yard TD

videos.description: Clayton Thorson's pass to Flynn Nagel hits off his hand, trickles off a Nebraska defender, and ends up in the arms of Tre Neal who returns Thorson's second pick 14 yards into Northwestern territory.
videos.headline: Thorson throws second interception

videos.description: Northwestern marches down the field behind an impressive drive orchestrated by Clayton Thorson, who whips a 5-yard touchdown to JJ Jefferson, tying the game at 31-31 with 12 seconds remaining.
videos.headline: Northwestern TD ties game with 12 seconds remaining

videos.description: Nebraska's Adrian Martinez is picked off by JR Pace in overtime in the end zone.
videos.headline: Pace comes up with huge INT for Northwestern in OT
